data.description: :Charming 1960s ranch on a great corner lot in Oak Grove community. Beautiful hardwood floors greet you in the living room, there are hardwoods under the carpet in the hallway and master bedroom.. Newer windows and blinds. There is a large deck in back with privacy fenced yard. Mature landscape and ready to move in. Home is located across the street from Pittman School and Holy Trinity Catholic church.
